### Create third test user (CONTRIBUTOR role)
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/signup
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Invite {{contributorInviteToken2}}

{
  "username": "thirduser",
  "email": "third@diariolx.pt",
  "password": "ThirdPass123!",
