### ===== STEP 6: GET USER INFO =====

### Get admin user info (as admin, using session token cookie)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/{{adminId}}
Cookie: token={{adminToken}}

###
### Get test user info (as test user)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/{{testUserId}}
Cookie: token={{testToken}}

###
### Get admin info (as test user)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/{{adminId}}
Cookie: token={{testToken}}

###
### Get user info with invalid ID (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/9999
Cookie: token={{testToken}}

### ===== STEP 7: LIST ALL USERS =====

### Get all users (include deactivated, pagination offset=0, limit=10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/all?offset=0&limit=10&deactivated=true
Cookie: token={{adminToken}}

###
### Get active users only (exclude deactivated, pagination offset=0, limit=5)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/all?offset=0&limit=5&deactivated=false
Cookie: token={{testToken}}

###
### Get users with different pagination (offset=1, limit=3)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/all?offset=1&limit=3&deactivated=true
Cookie: token={{adminToken}}

### ===== STEP 8: UPDATE USER PROFILE =====

### Update test user profile (all fields)
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/update
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token={{testToken}}

{
  "username": "testuser_updated",
  "email": "testuser.updated@diariolx.pt",
  "password": "UpdatedPass123!",
  "fName": "Test",
  "lName": "Updated",
  "bio": "I am a test user with a bio",
  "profilePictureURL": "https://example.com/avatar.jpg"
}

###
### Get test user info (as test user)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/{{testUserId}}
Cookie: token={{testToken}}

