### ===== STEP 14: LOGOUT =====

### Admin logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/logout
Cookie: token={{adminToken}}

###
### Test user logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/logout
Cookie: token={{testToken}}

###
### Try to access user info after logout (should fail - 401 UNAUTHORIZED)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/{{testUserId}}
Cookie: token={{testToken}}

###
### Editor logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/logout
Cookie: token={{editorToken}}

###
### Third user logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/logout
Cookie: token={{thirdToken}}
